{"tid":738186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版《你的名字》】港鐵廣告向日本動畫致敬？","createTime":"2018-07-11T10:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T10:19:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7abfec1bf9090a7c9453240800669d8576ec0b77","tid":738186,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵近日正式推出宣傳片段《他和她的第一次對話》，動畫畫風與日本動畫大師新海誠《你的名字》勁相似<br />\n<br />\n港鐵近日正式推出宣傳片段《他和她的第一次對話》，短短分半鐘的動畫以清新柔和畫風為主，並穿插各種漫畫化的實境背景。唔少香港人睇到都會覺得似曾相識，但未必係因為日日搭港鐵，而係呢啲畫風同日本動畫大師新海誠《你的名字》勁相似，咁到底係巧合，定係港鐵特意向《你的名字》致敬呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bka.mpweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Untitled-collage-30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FUntitled-collage-30.jpg&h=ca226c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 撇開劇情，香港版《你的名字》海報最為人熟悉就是主角身後蔚藍色的天空，配上清晰的白色文字 。港鐵宣傳片中亦同樣利用藍天作為影片的導入背景，一樣是寫上正楷白色的文字「他和她的第一次對話」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bka.mpweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Untitled-collage-2-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FUntitled-collage-2-4.jpg&h=97643b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實港鐵早在二零一七年開始流行這類日本漫畫的風格的乘客提示海報，例如提示乘客感到不適可找職員協助和讓座給有需要的人士等。可是，大批網民卻批評「抄完又要劣化埋」等言論 ，認為港鐵抄襲成份高，毫無創意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/20180711-122416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Ffocus%2F20180711-122416&d=cF0kG%2FC%2BtY7f1f5ux8Fd15nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=d6368662\" target=\"_blank\">https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/20180711-122416</a>"},{"pid":"801d4c37600a0a5ddeb638c0ccda36bcc81ddfdc","tid":738186,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"港豬最叻左抄右抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21432967434dd374e72d454e57fea6f2f4ef586","tid":738186,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}